00:23:48.159 --> 00:23:50.028
You are the only four here at
this moment.

00:23:50.061 --> 00:23:52.163
There was never another team
doing anything.

00:23:52.196 --> 00:23:53.397 line:0%
[man 1]

00:23:53.431 --> 00:23:57.569
This is a study related to
the Stanford Prison Experiment.

00:23:57.602 --> 00:23:58.870 line:0%
[man 1]

00:23:58.903 --> 00:24:01.139
The standard narrative
we hear about that experiment

00:24:01.172 --> 00:24:04.843 size:56% position:28%
is that people
just become cruel.

00:24:04.876 --> 00:24:08.680
So, yeah, we're trying to see if
we get the nicest people we can,

00:24:08.713 --> 00:24:10.715 size:78% position:39%
and we give them complete
anonymity

00:24:10.748 --> 00:24:15.854 size:88% position:44%
and the ability to be cruel,
but never encourage them to,

00:24:15.887 --> 00:24:17.188 align:start position:0%
will they still do it?

00:24:17.221 --> 00:24:18.857
And you guys didn't.

00:24:18.890 --> 00:24:22.126 size:84% position:42%
Did you have any suspicions
about what we were studying

00:24:22.159 --> 00:24:23.695 align:start position:0% line:0%
or what was going on?

00:24:31.102 --> 00:24:32.837 align:end size:59% position:59% line:0%
Right, but I think
that's good.

00:24:32.870 --> 00:24:34.639 size:78% position:39%
We just want to make sure
you don't think

00:24:34.672 --> 00:24:36.040 size:69% position:34%
that what we're really
looking at

00:24:36.073 --> 00:24:38.843 size:63% position:31%
is how high you turn
your own dial.

00:24:38.876 --> 00:24:41.613 size:69% position:34%
That's really
what we're looking at.

00:24:41.646 --> 00:24:44.649 line:0%
<i> It was time to bring in our
 second group of participants,</i>

00:24:44.682 --> 00:24:47.252 line:0%
<i> who, like the first group,
were screened to be individuals</i>

00:24:47.285 --> 00:24:49.921 line:0%
<i> with high morality
 characteristics.</i>

00:24:49.954 --> 00:24:52.891 align:start position:0% line:0%
Anything up to 7
should be safe.

00:24:54.792 --> 00:24:57.028
[laughs]
Yeah.

00:24:57.061 --> 00:24:57.962
[woman]
<i> So once I leave,</i>

00:24:57.996 --> 00:24:59.898
<i> you can go ahead
 and get started.</i>

00:24:59.931 --> 00:25:01.766 size:84% position:58% line:0%
[woman 1]

00:25:01.799 --> 00:25:03.034 line:0%
[laughs]

00:25:12.009 --> 00:25:13.177
Oh...

00:25:13.210 --> 00:25:14.779
[high-pitched squeal]

00:25:18.683 --> 00:25:21.319
Right off the bat she went to 7
and pushed the button.

00:25:21.352 --> 00:25:22.153 align:start position:0%
Yeah.

00:25:22.887 --> 00:25:25.156
[loud, discordant horn]

00:25:25.189 --> 00:25:27.091
[high-pitched squeal]

00:25:27.124 --> 00:25:29.561
[Michael]
Number two's pushing it at a 3.

00:25:30.962 --> 00:25:33.197
[discordant horn blares]

00:25:33.230 --> 00:25:35.700 size:84% position:58% line:0%
[woman 1]

