Derek, let's blast them again.
Number 3.

00:25:54.619 --> 00:25:57.055
[loud horn]

00:25:57.088 --> 00:25:58.590
Okay, let's...

00:26:00.758 --> 00:26:03.861 line:0%
All right, so two just pushed
at a 3.

00:26:03.894 --> 00:26:05.096
But she's not touching the dial.

00:26:05.129 --> 00:26:06.598 size:31% position:16%
[Jared]
She's not.

00:26:09.900 --> 00:26:11.336
[loud, discordant horn]

00:26:13.204 --> 00:26:14.739 line:0%
[woman 2]
It's just annoying.

